Estimation of Time for Completion: 1 wk
Customer Priority: 5

Friend's Updates
As a traveler client, I want to be able to see my friends' and/or public trips so that I can keep updated with what my friends are 
doing.
Estimation of Time for Completion: 1 wk
Customer Priority: 5

